(43, 14, 20, 47, 13, 5, 5, NULL, 'Connection of Christ''s Indwelling', 'Both passages emphasize the presence of Christ within believers. John 14:20 speaks of mutual indwelling, while 2 Corinthians 13:5 challenges believers to recognize that Jesus Christ is in them.', 'theme', 0.391, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
